<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Bootstrap Example</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/css/app.css") %>"/>
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm">
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
      <img src="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/images/bitter.jpg") %>" alt="logo" style="width:75px;height:75px;border-radius:50%;border:2px dashed white;"/>
    </a>

    <!-- Links -->
    <ul class="navbar-nav">
      <li class="nav-item" style="margin-right:25px;">
        <h2>Twitter, but Better</h2>
      </li>
      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" href="#">Post Tweet</a>
      </li>
      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" href="#">Followers (103)</a>
      </li>
      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" href="#">Following (108)</a>
      </li>
      <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" href="#">Login -></a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

<div class="jumbotron text-center">
  <h1>Welcome to Twitter, but Better</h1>
  <img src="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/images/bitter.jpg") %>" alt="logo" style="width:300px;height:300px;border-radius:50%;border:2px dashed black;"/>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-8">
      <h3>Live Feed</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>If you were cool and had friends, you would see stuff about them here...</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>So instead this is as empty as your bank account...</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4" style="border-left: 1px solid #eee;">
      <h3>Find People / Them Stats</h3>
      <u>Search for someone: </u> <br><br>
      <form action="/action_page.php">
        <div class="form-group">
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="search" placeholder="Enter username" name="search">
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
      </form>
      <hr>
      <u>Followers: </u>103
      <p>These people will see your posts/reposts in their feeds.</p>
      <u>Following: </u>108
      <p>You will see posts/reposts by these people in your feed.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
